(metatron . witness)

; Metatron alternating witness fixture.
;
; Registers:
;   witness = 0xAA55
;   inverse = 0x55AA
;
; Balance:
;   each register has 8 one bits and 8 zero bits
;
; XOR witnesses:
;   0xAA55 ^ 0x55AA = 0xFFFF
;   0xAA55 ^ 0xFFFF = 0x55AA
;   0x55AA ^ 0xFFFF = 0xAA55
;
; Authority:
;   Metatron witnesses/projections only after validation.
